        "meta_description": "Ishana Night Shyamalan, 24, makes her directorial debut with 'The Watchers,' in theaters now. She tells PEOPLE she 'always' took one piece of advice from her director father M. Night Shyamalan 'very seriously.'",
        "meta_lang": "en",
